    dc:description "Figure 1. Allorhogas conostegia Marsh and Shaw, female. (A) Head, anterior view (scale bar 0.3 mm); (B) head, dorsal lateral view (scale bar 0.3 mm); (C) mesosoma, dorsal view (scale bar 0.5 mm); (D) mesopleuron, lateral view (scale bar 0.3 mm); (E) metasoma, dorsal view (scale bar 0.3 mm); (F) ovipositor, lateral view (scale bar 0.03 mm)." ;
